---
import LeadsForm from "./LeadsForm.astro";

---
<div class="relative flex flex-col w-full h-auto justify-evenly items-center bg-main-orange overflow-hidden">
    <span class="hidden md:flex md:absolute left-8 -top-5 w-40 h-40 rounded-full bg-light-orange/40"></span>
    <span class="hidden md:flex md:absolute right-5 -bottom-25 w-50 h-50 rounded-full bg-light-orange/40"></span>
    <h2 class="w-[80%] md:w-[50%] text-center text-white font-bold font-[montserrat] text-2xl md:text-4xl mt-5">¿Listo para impulsar tu marca?</h2>
    <p class=" w-[70%] md:w-full text-white text-center text-lg font-[montserrat]">Solicita una consulta gratuita y descubre cómo podemos ayudarte</p>
    <LeadsForm />
    <ul class="flex flex-row justify-around items-center gap-x-10 w-[90%] md:w-full h-10 text-white font-[montserrat] font-semibold text-[10px] md:text-sm"> 
        <li class="w-[50%] h-auto text-center z-10">Sin compromiso</li>
        <li class="w-[50%] h-auto text-center z-10">Respuesta en 24 horas</li>
    </ul>
</div>